content: Very handy app to calculate mortgage payment when talking to a client. I love it.
Finally, a mortgage calculator thats mobile. Dev contacted me right away and resolved my issue. Thank you!!
replyContent: Hi, the issue has now been fixed. Sorry for the inconveniences that it causes. Thank you for taking the time to report the issue to us.

content: This app is simple, but allow you to calculate almost everything of a possible mortgage. It help me a lot in the process of seeing the potential of a house due to cost, interes, down payment, taxes, insurances, and extras. It is a simple and not fancy interface, but due the job. The best is that allow me to save everything in PDF.

Great app EXCEPT for the fact I cannot save my current entries in the app. Big fail, especially for the PRO edition. You should be able to save entries in the app and go back to them time after time until you change the entries or clear them.
Great - Great app. I even payed to remove ads to support it. Even with ads this was great..
Easy to use. Plug in your numbers and swipe right.
Love it! It really solves a lot of questions superbly! Thank you!
Easy to use and very helpful

It is a great tool to use for lowering your 30 yrs, 20 yrs, etc mortgage. I give the app 4 stars because I am not able to save and/or maintain what I just calculated in the app. It will be an amazing tool if we could keep whatever we set up within the app so we can make changes along the way. Overall, it is a good app!!!
